• Utilities within and adjacent to the proposed subdivision project; location, sizes and invert elevations of sanitary and storm or combined sewers; location of gas lines, fire hydrants, electric and telephone poles and street lights, if any. If water mains and sewers are not within or adjacent to the subdivision, indicate the direction and distance to and size of nearest one, showing invert elevations of sewers, if applicable.


